-----------------------------------------------------------
                     Pool of Radiance
                  Spell Parameters Chart
-----------------------------------------------------------
 
The following list collates all of the basic parameters of
the spells availible in Pool of Radiance...

------------------------------------------------------------

Spell Name                  Range       Duration       Where
------------------------------------------------------------

First level
Clerical Spells
------------------------------------------------------------

