Third Level
Magic User Spells
------------------------------------------------------------

Blink                       0           1 rnd/lvl       C
Dispel Magic                12          Permanent      E,C
Fireball                    10+1/lvl    -               C
Haste                       6           3+1 rnd/lvl     C
Hold Person                 12          2 rnds/lvl      C
Invisibility 10' Rad        Touch       Until Attack   E,C
